---
import ContentPage from "../../../components/ContentPage.astro";
import ContentPanel from "../../../components/ContentPanel.astro";
---

<ContentPage
  title="House rules | Tiny Temptation Tubs"
  lang="en"
  path="/en/rules/"
  heading="Rules"
  wide
  centerBody={false}
>
  <ContentPanel>
    <div class="hand-text flex flex-col gap-6">
      <h2>Venue &amp; Server Rules</h2>
      <p>
        To ensure a safe, relaxed, and enjoyable experience for everyone, the
        following house rules apply within our bathhouse.<br />
        By entering the venue, you agree to read, understand, and follow these rules.
      </p>
      <h3>1. General Conduct</h3>
      <p>
        Treat all guests with respect.<br />
        No hate, harassment, bullying, discrimination, or drama. Hate speech results
        in an instant ban.<br />
        NO means NO - always and without exception.
      </p>
      <h3>2. Chat &amp; Community Rules</h3>
      <p>
        No spam, flooding, or ping abuse.<br />
        No mic spam or intentionally loud or disruptive noises.<br />
        Stay on topic in the appropriate channels.<br />
        No advertisements unless approved by staff.<br />
        No illegal, harmful, or disruptive content.<br />
        Respect privacy - no doxxing or sharing personal information.<br />
        <strong class="highlight"
          >The usage and advertisement of Loporrit Sync is strongly discouraged!
          As adult Lalafell you have nothing to worry on Lightless!</strong
        >
      </p>
      <h3>3. Age Requirement</h3>
      <p>
        This is an 18+ venue!<br />
        Entry is only allowed if both real age and roleplay age are 18+.<br />
        <strong class="highlight"
          >The Kitten Body, any variation of it using C+, as well as any
          depiction of an underage character will be immediately banned and
          reported to Lightless!</strong
        >
      </p>
      <h3>4. Races &amp; Roleplay</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>All</strong> races are welcome <strong>including</strong> Lalafell.
        The same rules apply to everyone.<br />
        Nudity is allowed and encouraged.<br />
        ERP is allowed as long as it is consensual and follows the general rules.<br
        />
        Sexual animations are allowed, however:<br />
        – Please keep ERP chat in private.<br />
        – Do not involve others without their explicit consent.<br />
        – Do not take sexual roleplay to extreme levels in public areas.
      </p>
      <h3>5. Emotes, Pets &amp; Items</h3>
      <p>
        Please deactivate emote logs.<br />
        Only use weapons or pets if they fit your RP character.
      </p>
      <h3>6. Rooms &amp; Usage</h3>
      <p>
        Rooms may be used freely.<br />
        If staff requires a room for massages or photos, please vacate it when asked.
      </p>
      <h3>7. Enforcement</h3>
      <p>
        Staff reserves the right to take appropriate action in case of rule
        violations.<br />
        Repeated or severe violations may result in a permanent ban.<br />
        The staff team always has the final say.<br />
        Staff decisions must be respected and are not to be publicly argued or challenged.
      </p>
      <h3>8. NSFW</h3>
      <p>
        NSFW content is only permitted in designated NSFW areas. These areas are
        open to all races, including Lalafell. Access to NSFW areas and the
        required role are granted exclusively by the Owner or Co-Owner. We try
        our best to make sure there won't come a reporting wave based on our
        server so you can post freely and without fear<br />
        NSFW content outside these areas is not allowed.
      </p>
    </div>
  </ContentPanel>
</ContentPage>
